title: I-Doser V5 Premium 150 doses+ 232 unofficial doses Win+ Android
description:
This is Idoser V5 Premium ,i also put two more softwares working
with SBG files.

For Windows 
you can either install IDoser and play the Doses from "Doses Files" 
or install SBagen and open the files in "SBG Files"

For Android 
you need to install Binaural Player and you run the doses in SBG Files

( There is an IDoser Version for Android but since you cant get all doses
in cracked version for free I converted all doses (DRG files) to SBG file 
so you can run it in both Windows and Android )

I only converted official doses ,for the other doses you can convert them in
www.khattam.info/drg2sbg
